data.description: Discover the perfect blend of charm and comfort in this inviting ranch-style home, ideally tucked away in a quiet cul-de-sac. The home's welcoming bay windows lead into the spacious living area with vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace. Additional features include a covered rear deck, finished garage, and a parking area for a small boat or trailer. Come tour today!
